{"tid":583984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 有汗出無糧出？中國聯通零售員工疑被拖佣金　料逾70名員工受影響","createTime":"2018-03-07T12:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T04:29:52.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1594574e2381973f77a16968c6afccfb767ee3ce","tid":583984,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T12:48:51.000Z","msg":"公司電郵通知指　佣金將延遲8日發放<br />\n<br />\n電訊商中國聯通前線零售部員工衛先生（化名）指，自己從事電訊業零售工作逾十載，於兩年前轉到中國聯通工作。他坦言，任職零售員底薪低，<span style=\"color: red;\">月薪僅得7千至8千港元</span>，普遍都是以賺取佣金維生。<br />\n<br />\n衛先生續道，過往公司都會隔一個月發放佣金，如今年1月的佣金理應會在2月最後的一天支付，即是2月28日。他稱，上月27日突然收到公司內部電郵通知指，因公司出現「事故」，1月份的佣金將會延至3月8日才發放，但底薪支付安排則維持不變。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/164989/%E6%9C%89%E6%B1%97%E5%87%BA%E7%84%A1%E7%B3%A7%E5%87%BA-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%81%AF%E9%80%9A%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E7%96%91%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%96%E4%BD%A3%E9%87%91-%E6%96%99%E9%80%BE70%E5%90%8D%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%8F%97%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F164989%2F%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25B1%2597%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B3%25A7%25E5%2587%25BA-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2581%25AF%25E9%2580%259A%25E9%259B%25B6%25E5%2594%25AE%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%2596%2591%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2596%25E4%25BD%25A3%25E9%2587%2591-%25E6%2596%2599%25E9%2580%25BE70%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF&d=yfStLp%2FTRVbgmmFJcqg0PwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=27216019\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/164989/%E6%9C%89%E6%B1%97%E5%87%BA%E7%84%A1%E7%B3%A7%E5%87%BA-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%81%AF%E9%80%9A%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E7%96%91%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%96%E4%BD%A3%E9%87%91-%E6%96%99%E9%80%BE70%E5%90%8D%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%8F%97%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF</a>"},{"pid":"e227c446e70c50bcfb6d8538f10fadee61df0ddd","tid":583984,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"